---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Contact
description: Contact Sepideh Mansouri for UI/UX opportunities and collaborations.
---
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-copy">
    <p class="eyebrow">Contact</p>
    <h1>Let’s talk about design roles, internships, or thoughtful digital products.</h1>
    <p class="page-lead">{{ site.contact.intro }}</p>
    <p>{{ site.contact.availability }}</p>
  </div>
  <div class="page-hero-visual visual-swatch visual-swatch-sand">
    <span>Email</span>
    <strong>{{ site.author.email }}</strong>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="contact-grid">
  <article class="contact-card">
    <p class="eyebrow">Email</p>
    <h2><a href="mailto:{{ site.author.email }}">{{ site.author.email }}</a></h2>
    <p>The best place to reach me for roles, portfolio conversations, and collaboration inquiries.</p>
  </article>

  {% for item in site.social %}
    <article class="contact-card">
      <p class="eyebrow">{{ item.name }}</p>
      <h2><a href="{{ item.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">{{ item.url | replace("https://www.", "") | replace("https://", "") }}</a></h2>
      <p>Connect with me and explore more of my background and work.</p>
    </article>
  {% endfor %}

  <article class="contact-card">
    <p class="eyebrow">Resume</p>
    <h2><a href="{{ site.contact.resumePdf }}">Download PDF</a></h2>
    <p>Get the printable version of my resume generated from the same structured resume source as this website.</p>
  </article>
</section>
